reviewText: The music is nice, but some of the footage is used multiple times on the same disc, In "Colors of Christmas" The same footage of poinsettias was used 9 times! Every time I turned around, it was: (5min) Poinsettias, one Christmas tree, (5min) Poinsettias, a house,(5min) Poinsettias, a snowman, (5min) Poinsettias. You get the point.
